description: "On this map of Java, mountains are shown pictorially and labelled with their name. The coasts are marked with shoals, reefs, bathymetry (sea depth, in figures) and anchor points. The land is divided into administrative districts."
title: "Nouvelle Carte de l'isle de Java : dressée suivant les observations les plus recentes, faites par ordre de la Comp.Holl. des Indes Orientales"
